## Syntax:	acmbuild [ -h || --help || -V || --version ]		##
##									##
## Exit Codes:	0 & 64 - 113 as per C/C++ standard			##
##		0 - success						##
##		64 - Invalid arguments					##
##		65 - File(s) already exist				##
##		67 - trap received					##
