## 13/11/2014	MG	1.0.4	Switched from getopts to GNU getopt to	##
##				allow long options.			##
## 16/11/2014	MG	1.0.5	Modify getopt processing to allow for	##
##				FreeBSD's quirk of 2 different getopt	##
##				programs. See comments at the start of	##
